## Description {#details}

This is a type descriptor which explains the type requirements of an intrinsic.

This is returned by getIntrinsicInfoTableEntries.

Definition at line 131 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/intrinsics-h">Intrinsics.h</a>.
